#circuitbreakersg day 26

Homemade fettuccine alle vongole for dinner tonight. 😊
.
.
.
First time making pasta and really enjoyed the experience. And more importantly, the pasta turned out really well and has a nice bite. Will definitely be making more pasta soon! 😃
.
.
.
I am grateful today because I’m happy that the homemade pasta turned out great and that I enjoyed dinner. #gratitudediary
